summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the City Light Department accepting electrical underground and surface rights distribution easements over portions of Lots 13 and 14, Block 12, Capitol Hill Addition to the City of Seattle, Division No. 3; Lot 8, Block 28, Renton's Addition; Lot 9, Block 35, State Park Addition; Lot 7, Block 28, Renton's Addition; Parcel B of City of Seattle Short Plat 8606882 as recorded under King County Recording Number 9204060262; Lot 5, Block 33, Gilman's Addition; Section 6, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M.; and placing said easements under the jurisdiction of the City Light Department.
